# Sai Rapeti — Portfolio

A fast, responsive, single-page portfolio for showcasing projects, experience, and skills.  
**Live:** [rapetisai.github.io/sairapeti-portfolio](https://rapetisai.github.io/sairapeti-portfolio/)

<img alt="Portfolio preview" src="images/Project/landuse.png" width="640">

---

## Features
- 🎯 Clean single-page layout (About, Experience, Education, Skills, Projects, Contact)
- ⚡️ Pure static site (HTML/CSS/JS) — deploys easily on GitHub Pages
- 🌓 Dark mode toggle (template component)
- 🧩 Skills “logo cloud” using TagCanvas
- 🖼 Project cards with badges and screenshots
- 📄 One-click Resume link (PDF)

---

## Tech & Libraries
- [Bootstrap](https://getbootstrap.com/) (layout & utilities)  
- [Unicons](https://iconscout.com/unicons) (icons via `unicons.css`)  
- [Owl Carousel](https://owlcarousel2.github.io/OwlCarousel2/) (template dependency)  
- [TagCanvas](https://www.goat1000.com/tagcanvas.php) (spinning skills cloud)

> **Attribution:** Visual design inspired by [Syona Jaimy’s portfolio](https://syonajosy.github.io/syona-portfolio/).

